quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  3,71,ae ehley kitaab tum sach ko jhoot ke sath khalt malt kyun karte ho aur haq ko kyun chupatay ho aur tum jantay bhi ho
  3,72,aur ehley kitaab aik dosray se kehte hain ke jo ( kitaab ) mominoun par nazil hui hai is par din ke shuru mein to imaan le aaya karo aur is ke aakhir mein inkaar kar diya karo taakay woh ( islam se ) bur-ghashta ho jayen
  3,73,aur apne deen ke pairo ke siwa kisi aur ke qaail nah hona ( ae paighambar ) keh do ke hadaayat to khuda hi ki hadaayat hai ( woh yeh bhi kehte hain ) yeh bhi ( nah maanna ) ke jo cheez tum ko mili hai waisi kisi aur ko miley gi ya woh tumhe khuda ke rubaroo qaail maqool kar saken ge yeh bhi keh do ke buzurgi khuda hi ke haath mein hai woh jisay chahta hai deta hai aur khuda kashaish wala ( aur ) ilm wala hai
  3,74,woh apni rehmat se jis ko chahta hai khaas kar laita hai aur khuda barray fazl ka maalik hai
  3,75,aur ehley kitaab mein se koi to aisa hai ke agar tum is ke paas ( rupoo ka ) dhair amanat rakh do to tum ko ( foran ) wapas day day aur koi is terhan ka hai ke agar is ke paas aik dinar bhi amanat rakho to jab taq is ke sir par har waqt kharray nah raho tumhe day hi nahi yeh is liye ke woh kehte hain ke ummiyon ke baray mein hum se muwakhza nahi hoga yeh khuda par mehez jhoot boltay hain aur ( is baat ko ) jantay bhi hain
  3,76,haan jo shakhs apne iqraar ko poora kere aur ( khuda se ) daray to khuda darny walon ko dost rakhta hai
  3,77,jo log khuda ke iqraron aur apni qasmon ( ko beech daaltay hain aur un ) ke aiwz thori si qeemat haasil karte hain un ka akhirat mein kuch hissa nahi un se khuda nah to kalaam kere ga aur nah qayamat ke roz un ki taraf dekhe ga aur nah un ko pak kere ga aur un ko dukh dainay wala azaab hoga
